        /// <br/> *  `SERVICEDESK_AGENT` (Jira Service Desk only)
        /// <br/> *  `VIEW_DEV_TOOLS` (Jira Software only)
        /// <br/> *  `VIEW_READONLY_WORKFLOW`
        /// <br/>
        /// <br/>**Issue permissions**
        /// <br/>
        /// <br/> *  `ASSIGNABLE_USER`
        /// <br/> *  `ASSIGN_ISSUES`
        /// <br/> *  `CLOSE_ISSUES`
        /// <br/> *  `CREATE_ISSUES`
        /// <br/> *  `DELETE_ISSUES`
        /// <br/> *  `EDIT_ISSUES`
        /// <br/> *  `LINK_ISSUES`
